IRS990EZ.PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt: THE MISSION OF THE PRIEST LAKE CHAMBER OF COMMERCE IS TO PROMOTE ACTIVITIES TO SATISFY THE NEEDS OF ITS MEMBERS AND THE PRIEST LAKE COMMUNITY WHICH INCLUDES: 1. PROMOTE AND STRENGTHEN THE ECONOMIC CLIMATE OF THE PRIEST LAKE AREA 2. SUPPORT THE FREE ENTERPRISE SYSTEM 3. OPERATE ON A SOUND FINANCIAL BASIS 4. BROADEN THE MEMBERSHIP BASE 5. PROMOTE THE ENJOYMENT OF THE AREA'S NATURAL RESOURCES 6. PROMOTE RESPONSIBLE MANAGEMENT OF AND ACCESS TO THE AREA'S NATURAL RESOURCES AND PUBLIC LANDS 7. ENHANCE THE QUALITY OF LIFE AND MEET COMMUNITY NEEDS THE PRIEST LAKE CHAMBER OF COMMERCE MEMBERS ARE PART OF A STRONG COMMUNITY ORGANIZATION, WHICH SHARE THE GOAL OF IMPROVING THE QUALITY OF LIFE FOR ALL WHO EXPERIENCE PRIEST LAKE, WHETHER RESIDENTS OR VISITORS. THE CHAMBER VOLUNTEERS WORK VERY HARD TO PROMOTE BUSINESS WHILE ASSISTING VISITORS IN EXPERIENCING THE WONDER OF OUR PRIEST LAKE COMMUNITY THROUGH A VARIETY OF MARKETING PROJECTS EACH YEAR.

ProgramSrvcAccomplishmentGrp.DescriptionProgramSrvcAccomTxt: CURRENTLY SERVING 150 MEMBERS BY PROVIDING LISTINGS AND LINKS ON THE CHAMBER WEBSITE TO PROMOTE THEIR BUSINESSES. WE PRODUCE A FULL-COLOR PRIEST LAKE VISITORS GUIDE, PRINTING AND DISTRIBUTING APPROXIMATELY 25,000 COPIES THROUGHOUT THE NORTHWEST. WE PRINT A MONTHLY CALENDAR OF EVENTS AND A WEEKLY FLYER OF EVENTS AND ACTIVITIES DURING THE SUMMER MONTHS. WE PROVIDE TELEVISION ADVERTISEMENT AS WELL AS ADVERTISING IN VARIOUS LOCAL AND NATIONAL MAGAZINES. WE ASSIST WITH PROMOTING THE SPRING FESTIVAL HELD IN COOLIN ON MEMORIAL DAY WEEKEND, THE HUCKLEBERRY FESTIVAL HELD IN JULY, THE SNOW SHOE SOFTBALL TOURNAMENT HELD IN JAN-FEB, THE PRIEST LAKE MARATHON AND TRIATHLON, AS WELL AS ANY OTHER ACTIVITIES THAT WILL HELP BUSINESSES GROW THEIR EXPOSURE AND SUCCESS. WE WILL CONTINUE TO FOCUS ON INCREASING BOTH OUR BUSINESS AND ASSOCIATE MEMBERSHIP AS IT GIVES NON-PROFITS AND INDIVIDUALS A CHANCE TO SUPPORT THE CHAMBER'S EFFORTS. OUR WEBSITE PROVIDES A PLACE FOR OUR LOCAL BUSINESSES TO ADVERTISE ON THE WEB AND WE SUPPORT SEVERAL WEBSITES WHICH HAVE LINKS TO OUR WEBSITE. WE WORK CLOSELY WITH OTHER ORGANIZATIONS TO SPONSOR A VERY SUCCESSFUL SPRING FESTIVAL WEEKEND INCLUDING THE PEOPLE HELPING PEOPLE AUCTION. WE PROVIDE A WEEKLY "THIS WEEK AT THE LAKE" FLYER FOR ACTIVITIES AND EVENTS ALL SUMMER WHICH HELPS OUR VISITORS DISCOVER NEW WAYS TO ENJOY OUR AREA. ON BEHALF OF THE PRIEST LAKE AREA, WE FUND AND SUPPLY THE MEANS FOR THE LAKE TO BE REPRESENTED AT SEVERAL TRADE SHOWS, INCLUDING SNOWMOBILE SHOWS AND BOAT SHOWS. WE PROVIDE A FORUM FOR THE LOCAL COMMUNITY TO BECOME INFORMED ON ISSUES SUCH AS THE CRITICAL HABITAT OF THE CARIBOU BY HOLDING MEETINGS WITH SPEAKERS WHO PRESENT THE ISSUES AND ANSWER QUESTIONS.
